  "name": "Half-Distance Power Development",
  "note": "This session is designed to develop your half-distance triathlon power. For most people half-distance triathlon power is at around 83% of FTP, and we will aim to improve this power by working slightly above and slightly below this power target for extended periods. \n\nThis is a pyramid set, 1 x 8 mins, 1 x 6 mins, 2 x 4 mins, 1 x 6 mins and 1 x 8 mins, with 36 minutes of total work. (by Coach Dan Plews)",
